- @kpd_wins: The communists have been elected.
- @sapd_wins: The SAPD has been elected.
- @spd_wins: We have won!
- @independent_wins: The independents have been elected.
- @bourgeois_wins: The bourgeois have been elected.
- @nsdap_wins: The Nazis have been elected.
- @spd_campaign_hq: What can we do?
- @other_forces: The other forces make their moves...

